---
import SectionTitles from '../../layouts/mini-layouts/SectionTitles.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import m_m5 from '../../assets/m_m5.png';
---

<section class='about' id='about'>
  <SectionTitles
    titleSmall='O SamoZUO'
    titleBig='Przeczytaj, to lepiej mnie poznasz!'
  />
  <div>
    <div class='image-wrapper'>
      <Image class='image' src={m_m5} alt='man' />
    </div>
    <div class='text-wrapper'>
      <p class='quote'>
        "The way you teach is more important than what you are teaching"
      </p>
      <p class='text'>
        Jestem SamoZUO marketingu i sprzedaży B2B. Nie jestem agencją
        marketingową. Nie jestem firmą reklamową - jakie pewnie znasz i z jakimi
        się zetknąłeś. Wyciągam z czarnej dupy firmy małe, bardzo duże, średnie
        i mikroprzedsiębiorców – ale to wtedy kiedy tam się znalazły.
      </p>
      <p class='text'>
        Moim klientom robię dobrze bo…dowożę im wyniki i pomagam ogarniać ich
        firmę za hajs i cuba librę – ale zawsze dla nich i dla mnie...<a
          href='/about'
          class='text-link'> Czytaj dalej</a
        >
      </p>
      <!-- <a href='/about' class='button-link'>Czytaj dalej</a> -->
      <div class='social-wrapper'>
        <a
          href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/coachsamozuo-maciek-aloha-marketing-0739a924a/'
          class='social-icon'
          aria-label='Link to linkedin'
          ><i class='fa-brands fa-linkedin-in'></i></a
        >
        <a
          href='https://www.facebook.com/doradcaCoachconsultant'
          class='social-icon'
          aria-label='Link to Facebook'
          ><i class='fa-brands fa-facebook-f'></i></a
        >
        <a
          href='https://www.tiktok.com/@maciekmartowicz'
          class='social-icon'
          aria-label='Link to tik-tok'><i class='fa-brands fa-tiktok'></i></a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 25px 25px 65px 25px;
    background-color: var(--base-white);
  }
  .image-wrapper {
    max-width: 100vw;
  }
  .image {
    border-radius: 7px;
    object-fit: contain;
    width: 100%;
    height: fit-content;
  }
  .quote {
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-family: var(--font_3);
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    opacity: 0.4;
    /* text-align: center; */
    color: var(--light-violet);
  }
  .text {
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    line-height: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--second-font);
    margin: 20px 0;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--violet);
  }
  .text-link {
    color: var(--base-orange);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: .2s all ease-in;
  }
  .text-link:hover {
    
    color: var(--light-violet);
  }
  .button-link {
    width: fit-content;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 25px 0 25px 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--dark-violet);
    padding: 10px 60px;
    /* border: 1px solid var(--dark-violet); */
    outline: 1px solid var(--dark-violet);
    border-radius: 19px;
    font-family: var(--second-font);
    transition: 0.2s all ease-in;
  }
  .button-link:hover {
    color: var(--base-white);
    outline: transparent;
    background-color: var(--base-orange);
  }
  .social-wrapper {
    gap: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }
  .social-icon {
    position: relative;
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 19px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--base-orange);
    transition: 0.3s background-color ease;
  }
  .social-icon:hover {
    background-color: var(--light-violet);
  }
  .fa-brands {
    position: absolute;
    padding: 19px;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    color: var(--base-white);
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .image-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    .image {
      width: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
    }
    div {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 120px;
    }
    .text-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0;
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 600px;
    }
    .text {
      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1vw, 1.5rem);
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .text::first-letter {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--base-orange);
      font-weight: 900;
    }
    .quote {
      text-align: left;
      /* max-width: 500px; */
      font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 2vw, 2.5rem);
      opacity: 0.3;
    }
    .social-wrapper {
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 70px;
    }
  }
</style>
